  "shortName": "koo-fortuny____",
  "description": "<i>Ko?o Fortuny</i>  is a video game based on the Polish edition of the TV game show of the same name (similar to the English <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Wheel+of+Fortune\">Wheel of Fortune</a>). Players take turns guessing letters to form a word or a saying. It can be played with up to three players. They have the option of playing with or without computer players giving contestants the ability to go head-to-head in a game against a friend. After each winning round the player may buy a gift prize. The game is divided into three rounds all together, two for eliminations and the third one as the final.",
